    "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\ninvalid regex pattern will raise NPE\r\n```java\r\njava.lang.NullPointerException: null\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\ncatch `PatternSyntaxException` while compiling the regexp pattern by the `regexp_extract`, `regexp_extract_all` and `regexp_instr`, and substitute the exception by Spark's exception w/ the error class `INVALID_PARAMETER_VALUE`. In this way, Spark SQL will output the error in the form:\r\n```sql\r\norg.apache.spark.SparkRuntimeException\r\n[INVALID_PARAMETER_VALUE] The value of parameter(s) 'regexp' in `regexp_instr` is invalid: ) ?\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n\r\n- spark-3.4: https://github.com/apache/spark/commit/5b96bd5cf8\r\n- spark-3.3: https://github.com/apache/spark/commit/0e2758c995\r\n- spark-3.2: https://github.com/apache/spark/commit/ea5af851e7\r\n",
